title: Local News: Upgrade: Talented Dela working with Nigeria's renowned director Clarence Peters
text:
Upgrade: Talented Dela working with Nigeria's renowned director Clarence Peters By Njambi Mungai Thursday, Oct 22nd 2015 at 12:24 
Taurus Musik not only signed the beautiful and talented Dela but also rebranded her to a classy, sensual and mature Afro pop artist. 
On top of her collaborating with major international acts, Dela was spotted with the multiple award winning Nigerian music video director and cinema photographer Clarence Peters. 
“I am very excited about this project, working with Clarence has always been one of my dreams and I am glad Taurus Musik has made it come true, this is just the beginning of bigger projects are to come. Watch this space,” Dela said.
